description: Erection of a building accommodating 680sqm A1/A2/A3/A4/D2 uses on the ground floor level and 83 residential units on the other levels with associated landscaped amenity atrium and amendments to the basement car park in place of the 976sqm Class A1 and 7,475 sqm Class B1 (Building 2) approved under 00505/P/P59 dated 8/12/06
